}

=head1 NAME

plotlc - Plot AR Lac light curve.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

plotlc file1.rdb file2.rdb ...

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Plot AR Lac light curve, given input  RDB files containing flux data.

=head1 OPTIONS

=over 4

=item --help

Show help and exit.

=item --version

Show version and exit.

=item --obsids=s

Code to eval for getting obsids.

=item --notcolor

Color points on vignette correction instead of time of obs.

=item --cmap=s

Which colormap to use for time coloring.

=item --norcmap

Do not reverse color map.

=item --nowedge

Do not plot a wedge annotation for time colors.

=item --hrci

Use HRC-I obsids.

=item --hrcs

Use HRC-S obsids.

=item --dev=s

PGPLOT device to use for final plot.

=item --flux

Plot fluxes instead of manually-corrected rates

=item --model=s

Which model to plot (default is "05").

=item --nopmodel

Do not plot the light curve model

=back

